cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.ET, cs.SE, cs.HC 

This paper discusses the ethical issues related to the use of artificial intelligence technology, which falls under the category of cs.AI. It also addresses the social impact of AI, which could be categorized under cs.CY. The paper proposes a technological framework for ethical engineering, which could be classified under cs.ET. The focus on ensuring social benefit and promoting trust aligns with the goals of cs.SE (software engineering) and cs.HC (human-computer interaction).
